video.title: Pee-wee's Playhouse
video.synopsis: Pee-wee Herman brings his stage show to the masses with this innovative live-action kids series that invites viewers into his quirky, childlike world.

episodes.synopsis: When Pee-wee's friends come by to swim in the Playhouse pool, he makes a big bowl of ice cream soup for everyone!
episodes.title: Ice Cream Soup

episodes.synopsis: Pee-wee wins a game show prize of a free Hawaiian dinner for two, but he doesn't know who to take as his guest.
episodes.title: Luau for Two

episodes.synopsis: On a rainy day, Pee-wee tries to keep everyone entertained by playing games, making hot chocolate, telling a ghost story and watching cartoons.
episodes.title: Rainy Day

episodes.synopsis: Pee-wee puts on a magic show and makes himself disappear! But when he can't make himself reappear, he'll need help from Jambi the Genie.
episodes.title: Now You See Me, Now You Don’t

episodes.synopsis: Cowboy Curtis shows Pee-wee how to square dance and pogo. Then everyone has a cowboy-style snack!
episodes.title: Just Another Day

episodes.synopsis: Miss Yvonne plans to give a makeover to the next person who walks into the Playhouse, and the lucky recipient is Mrs. Steve!
episodes.title: Beauty Makeovers

episodes.synopsis: Captain Carl orders everything on the menu at Pee-wee's restaurant, but it turns out they only have peanut butter and jelly sandwiches.
episodes.title: The Restaurant

episodes.synopsis: When the ants escape from their ant farm, the Playhouse is so overrun by ants that Pee-wee decides to do the Ants in Your Pants Dance.
episodes.title: Ants in Your Pants

episodes.synopsis: A giant monster scares everyone in the Playhouse, but once Pee-wee offers it a snack, the gang realizes they've found a new friend.
episodes.title: Monster in the Playhouse

episodes.synopsis: When Miss Yvonne asks Cowboy Curtis on a date, he's very nervous, so Cowntess enlists Pee-wee to help calm him down.
episodes.title: The Cowboy and the Cowntess

episodes.synopsis: When Randy steals Mrs. Steve's crummy crab apples from her tree, Pee-wee helps her find him, and there are plenty of apples for snack time.
episodes.title: Stolen Apples

episodes.synopsis: When the Playhouse gang visits, they all draw pictures of Pee-wee, and Pee-wee gives everyone secret names that end in "o."
episodes.title: The Gang’s All Here

episodes.synopsis: Join Cowboy Curtis, Captain Carl, Reba the Mail Lady and the lovely Miss Yvonne for a party at the Playhouse!
episodes.title: Party

episodes.synopsis: Pee-wee tricks his friends into doing his chores by pretending that work is fun, and the gang meets some new friends while renovating the Playhouse.
episodes.title: Open House

episodes.synopsis: Cowntess shows off her home movies from her cruise around the world. And when a lost puppy appears at the Playhouse door, Pee-wee decides to keep him.
episodes.title: Puppy in the Playhouse

episodes.synopsis: Pee-wee and Cowboy Curtis get chased by a train inside Magic Screen, and Cowboy Curtis and Miss Yvonne go shopping at Pee-wee's department store.
episodes.title: Store

episodes.synopsis: When Pee-wee is stuck inside with a cold, Nurse Yvonne and Ricardo come to the rescue with some good advice and chicken soup for their friend.
episodes.title: Pee-wee Catches a Cold

episodes.synopsis: When a caterpillar crawls into the flower box, the Magic Screen reveals how a caterpillar can turn itself into a beautiful butterfly.
episodes.title: Why Wasn't I Invited?

episodes.synopsis: Pee-wee shows off his lip-synching skills, Cowboy Curtis comes over and sings to the flowers and Miss Yvonne does a wild clog dance.
episodes.title: Tons of Fun

episodes.synopsis: Pee-wee turns the Playhouse into a schoolhouse and teaches his friends about Christopher Columbus and the Declaration of Independence.
episodes.title: School

episodes.synopsis: On the first day of spring, Pee-wee plants seeds and watches as they grow very quickly. The King of Cartoons visits and introduces his wife and son.
episodes.title: Spring

episodes.synopsis: The entire Playhouse is sucked into space, transported to a strange planet and taken over by an odd, lonely alien named Zyzzybalubah!
episodes.title: Playhouse in Outer Space

episodes.synopsis: Pee-wee and Miss Yvonne host a pajama party, and Pee-wee declares that since he loves his fruit salad so much, he's going to marry it!
episodes.title: Pajama Party

episodes.synopsis: Pee-wee's "urgent" need to have his letter mailed pulls Reba into work on her day off. Meanwhile, Pterri gets punished for bad behavior.
episodes.title: Reba Eats and Pterri Runs

episodes.synopsis: There's some serious pain on the premises when Pee-wee gets a terrible toothache and is forced to confront his fear of the dentist.
episodes.title: To Tell the Tooth

episodes.synopsis: Chandelier, Magic Screen and Pterri help Pee-wee give Reba an X-ray and take her temperature when she isn't feeling well.
episodes.title: Dr. Pee-wee and the Del Rubios

episodes.synopsis: When Pee-wee and Miss Yvonne are baking bread for sandwiches, Randy turns the temperature on Miss Yvonne's oven up to 700 degrees!
episodes.title: Fire in the Playhouse

episodes.synopsis: Miss Yvonne tells a wild story in hula, and when Magic Screen gives Pee-wee magic beans, they lead him into a giant adventure!
episodes.title: Love That Story

episodes.synopsis: When Jambi is sick, Pee-wee has to call a genie-ologist! It's Dr. Jinga-Janga to the rescue, but he's got a wacky bedside manner.
episodes.title: Sick, Did Someone Say Sick

episodes.synopsis: While her house is being painted, Miss Yvonne accepts an invitation to stay at the Playhouse -- but she's wearing too much perfume!
episodes.title: Miss Yvonne’s Visit

episodes.synopsis: Pee-wee and friends pretend to take a trip around the world, and Reba and her date go to a drive-in movie -- with Pee-wee and Miss Yvonne chaperoning!
episodes.title: Rebarella

episodes.synopsis: Miss Yvonne and Mrs. Rene face off in a trial presided over by Judge Pee-wee when they both wear the same one-of-a-kind dress.
episodes.title: Heat Wave

episodes.synopsis: Pee-wee and the gang round up things in the Playhouse that they don't use anymore so they can donate them to charity.
episodes.title: Chairry Tee Drive

episodes.synopsis: Pee-wee and Miss Yvonne are playing office and taking turns as boss and secretary. Later on, Cowboy Curtis stops by with a new friend: a cactus!
episodes.title: Let’s Play Office

episodes.synopsis: Pee-wee and friends think about fun times they've had with Cowboy Curtis, like when he showed off his rope tricks and went on a date with Miss Yvonne.
episodes.title: I Remember Curtis

episodes.synopsis: When Conky conks out and needs fixing fast, a desperate Pee-wee calls in a professional repairman. But Miss Yvonne's charms prove counterproductive.
episodes.title: Conky’s Breakdown

episodes.synopsis: There's a Playhouse mystery in the making when Pee-wee's suits go missing and his cereal bowl and spoon vanish into thin air.
episodes.title: Mystery

episodes.synopsis: Pee-wee's quest to print the Playhouse's first newspaper comes to a standstill when a meddling Randy tampers with the truth.
episodes.title: Front Page Pee-wee

episodes.synopsis: Mrs. Renee is determined to learn the tango with Pee-wee's help. But he proves to be an overzealous partner when he twirls her out of the Playhouse.
episodes.title: Tango Time

episodes.synopsis: Pee-wee and his friends celebrate "Playhouse Day," a dreamed-up holiday designed to get Cowboy Curtis, Miss Yvonne and Cowntess out of work.
episodes.title: Playhouse Day

episodes.synopsis: When a new friend from Japan stops by the Playhouse, Pee-wee learns about sushi, origami and understanding different cultures.
episodes.title: Accidental Playhouse

episodes.synopsis: Fun takes an unexpected turn when Pee-wee crafts a handmade mobile and Miss Yvonne teaches everyone how to make cheese balls.
episodes.title: Fun, Fun, Fun

episodes.synopsis: Mrs. Renee agrees to keep an eye on the Playhouse when Pee-wee goes camping with Cowboy Curtis to get a taste of the great outdoors.
episodes.title: Camping Out

episodes.synopsis: An aimless Pee-wee is looking for something to do when Jambi gives him a long list of options. But what will he decide to do first?
episodes.title: Something to Do

episodes.synopsis: When Miss Yvonne shows up to visit with Pee-wee, she finds a "For Sale" sign in the front yard but can't find Pee-wee anywhere.
episodes.title: Playhouse for Sale
